### Submit enrollment application
POST https://api.example.com/enrollment/applications
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: demo-correlation-id

{
  "guardian_email": "guardian@example.com",
  "guardian_phone": "+201234567890",
  "student_first_name": "Ali",
  "student_last_name": "Hassan",
  "checklist": {
    "birth_certificate": true,
    "vaccination_record": true,
    "proof_of_address": false
  },
  "metadata": {
    "preferred_language": "ar",
    "grade_level": "G07"
  }
}

### Approve enrollment application
PATCH https://api.example.com/enrollment/applications/{{application_id}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: demo-correlation-id

{
  "approved_by": "{{staff_id}}",
  "notes": "Reviewed on 18/02/2025",
  "assigned_student_code": "STU-001"
}
